{"tid":730621,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］點樣令家貓接受同居男朋友","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T13:16:06.000Z","uid":78668,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e298c78d9f87c016deb3ead61ea6b83b5f884f","tid":730621,"uid":78668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"家貓9個月大，以前一個人住由二個月養大<br />\n最近同男同居左一個月，隻貓成日無啦啦發脾氣咬得我好勁<br />\n成手成腳傷 仲有時無啦啦出貓拳打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身隻貓勁痴人同貪玩 超活潑<br />\n食飯訓覺去廁所都會跟住我<br />\n<br />\n男朋友都有同佢玩佢都肯玩，平時都唔係話驚佢同避開佢<br />\n不過比以前叫多左 成日喵喵喵<br />\n最慘有時會無啦啦會發脾氣咬人（但只係咬我）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底有咩辦法可以令佢地相處好d<br />\n唔想成日俾人咬同要關住佢或者打佢鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496f06b561ab9c98e7c96bc4aac715d50af6e918","tid":730621,"uid":78668,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/222924_5224f823440e6ed71b71f9c5bcb5e722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F222924_5224f823440e6ed71b71f9c5bcb5e722.jpg&h=504d14a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2425ed033a94b5e105931a3f87bba48110a3a0ad","tid":730621,"uid":78536,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"貓仔: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬲死你!!唔要我!!哼!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2374f0ab0516e9004ac42445299038a70cb81fb7","tid":730621,"uid":28277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05